post_text: Fire Prevention Week: The Edgewater and Fort Lee Fire Department visited EVG today. Students had the opportunity to practice fire safety by going into a simulation Smoke House. We appreciate the Edgewater and Fort Lee Fire Departments for providing this important training for our schools each year.

post_text: The Palisades Rotary provides weekend snack packs for our GW and EVG students from income-eligible families. Thank you, Rotarians!
shared_text:
Rotary Club of The Palisades
August 10, 2019 at 6:57 AM ·

The Rotary Club of The Palisades is pleased to announce the 20th anniversary of Oktoberfest in Leonia, NJ - the biggest fundrainser of our Rotary Club.
We are looking forward to an awesome event with music, dance acts, authentic German food and beer, a beer stemming contest and much more, stay tuned.

The American Legion in Leonia, NJ will transform into a beergarden and host the Oktoberfest rain/shine!
To pre-purchase tickets, please follow the link:
https://leoniaoktoberfest.square.site/
And more information can be found on our website: https://leoniaoktoberfest.com/

Get your drindls and lederhosn out of the closets and buy your early sale tickets, remember pre-sale $10 / by the door $15, kids up to 12 years of age are free.

Prost!
#LeoniaOktoberfest #RotaryPalisades #Fundraiser
